Yes, I too have been discriminated for being a girl. Had judgements thrown onto my face for being myself, wearing what I like and doing what I want. My advice, don’t let these judgements overpower you and rather use it to your power. I am very thankful to @JustHumanIndia who gave me this opportunity to put my story of discrimination  out in the world. This movement started by them is a great initiative and I hope they can reach out to everyone who has faced prejudice of any sorts. 
You can tell your story of discrimination too by using the hashtag #Iamjusthuman.
